### 1. 创建房源
POST http://localhost:8080/api/house/resource/create
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 2. 创建用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}


### 3. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. 获取当前用户资料
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 5. 更新当前用户资料
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "nickname": "好客用户",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "avatar": "avatars/example.png"
}


### 6. 上传头像
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file/avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=avatar-boundary

--avatar-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./avatar.png
--avatar-boundary--
